## üõ†Ô∏è Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- Python 3.10 or higher
- Git
- OpenAI API key
- (Optional) Claude Desktop for MCP integration

### Quick Start

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/nyalamrithwik-oss/RAG-MCP-learning.git
cd RAG-MCP-learning

# Create virtual environment
python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\activate  # Windows
source venv/bin/activate  # Linux/Mac

# Navigate to any project and install dependencies
cd day1-basic-rag
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Run the project
python basic_rag.py
```

### Exploring Week 2 MCP Servers

```bash
# Navigate to week2-mcp
cd week2-mcp

# Run unified demo
python DEMO_ALL_SERVERS.py

# Or explore individual servers
cd day8-mcp-basics
python simple_mcp_server.py
```

For complete MCP integration with Claude Desktop, see the **[MCP Integration Guide](./week2-mcp/MCP_INTEGRATION_GUIDE.md)**.

